api_list.name: Fetch a Business Profile by URL - JustDial API
api_list.description: Returns all Business Profile data from JustDial in JSON format
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://justdial-jd-unofficial.p.rapidapi.com/fetch_profile"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "justdial-jd-unofficial.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
